Vumela abasebenzisi ukuthi bengeze noma bakhiphe i-akhawunti ye-Exchange, ngaphandle kwe-akhawunti ecacisiwe kulokhu kulungiselela okulawuliwe. Uma lesi silungiselelo sinikezwe amandla, awukwazi ukuvimba abasebenzisi ukuze bengeze amanye ama-akhawunti e-Exchange ku-Gmail. Awukwazi futhi ukulawula ukwabelana ngedatha phakathi kwezinye izinhlelo zokusebenza kanye nama-akhawunti e-Exchange engezwe abasebenzisi. Lesi silungiselelo kufanele sinikezwe amandla kuphela uma abasebenzisi bedinga ukugcina i-akhawunti ye-Exchange engaphezu kweyodwa ku-Gmail.

Inani elisuka ku-0-5 elimelela iwindi lesikhathi sokuvumelanisa ne-EAS (I-Exchange ActiveSync). Ngokuzenzakalelayo iya evikini elilodwa (inani=3). [0=Asikho isihlungi, ivumelanisa zonke izinto. 1=usuku olungu-1. 2=izinsuku ezingu-3. 3=Iviki elingu-1. 4=amaviki angu-2. 5=inyanga engu-1.] Bona okuthi https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/gg709713(v=exchg.80).aspx ukuze uthole ulwazi oluphelele mayelana nezilungiselelo zewindi lokuvumelanisa.
Iyunithi yezinhlamvu eyakhiwa isiginesha ye-imeyili ezenzakalelayo ezokwengezwa ezansi kwawo wonke umbhalo womlayezo we-imeyili ephumayo.

Inkambu eshintshashintshayo esekela ikheli le-imeyili elithile (janedoe@company.com) noma inani lezifanekiso ($emailaddress$). Ama-EMM angakwazi ukusebenzisa le nkambu ukuze adonse ukuqinisekisa ukusuka ku-ActiveDirectory.

Iyunithi yezinhlamvu equkethe i-ID yedivayisi ye-EAS (I-Exchange ActiveSync), engase isetshenziswe amanye amasango e-EMM ukuze kuhlotshaniswe amadivayisi. (Lesi silungiselelo siyazitshwa lapho sisethwe ukuthi singabi nalutho noma i-akhawunti ye-Exchange isivele yethuliwe kuphrofayela elawuliwe).

Igama lomethuleli eliphelele leseva ye-ActiveSync, elifana nokuthi hostname.company.com:443/path. Igama lomethuleli lingafinyelelwa ngeseva eyibamba yesayithi ye-EMM, i-VIP (i-virtual IP) ephakela amaseva e-ActiveSync amaningi, noma ngokuqondile ku-CAS yasesidlangalaleni (iseva yokufinyelela kweklayenti). Umsingathi oshiwo akufanele aqondiswe kabusha komunye umsingathi. Iya ngokuzenzakalelayo embotsheni ethi 443 ngaphandle kwalapho kushiwo okuhlukile.

Isibizo seyunithi yezinhlamvu ezingezona ezingenalutho zesitifiketi sikakhiye oyimfihlo ogcinwe ku-keystore yephrofayela yomsebenzi uhlelo lokusebenza lwe-DPC ye-EMM esizosetshenziselwa ukufakazela ubuqiniso Bamaseva e-ActiveSync.

Inani lezimiso eziphusile elinikeza amandla futhi lidinge i-SSL ezinombolweni zembobo esetshenziswa Negama lomethuleli lapho limiswe ukuze lithi Iqiniso (ngokuzenzakalelayo). (Lesi silungiselelo sishaywa indiva lapho imbobo ethi 443 isetshenziswa kokuthi Igama lomethuleli).

Inani eliphusile lezimiso elikhubaza ukuhlola kokuqinisekisa kuzitifiketi ze-SSL ezisetshenziswa ekuxhumaneni okuphakathi kwamaseva e-ActiveSync, izimeleli, noma amasango, namanye amaseva e-imeyili. Misa ukuze ithi Iqiniso ukuze ukhubaze ukuhlola kokuqinisekisa lapho usebenzisa Izitifiketi ezizisayinayo noma ngokwezinjongo zokuhlola.
